@Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@Token = <your-access-token>

### Health Check
GET {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Current User (requires auth)
GET {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Get User Claims (requires auth)
GET {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/claims
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Read All Data (requires read:data scope)
GET {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/data/
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Write Data (requires write:data scope)
POST {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/data/
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "name": "New Item",
  "value": "New Value"
}

###

### Purge All Data (requires admin permission)
DELETE {{Auth0.Auth.Api_HostAddress}}/api/data/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###
